		<RichText x="66" y="762" width="499" height="97" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">蕴光之茧：暴击率<span color="#ffdfbf">-100%</span><span>，造成的伤害</span><span color="#ffdfbf">-50%</span><span>，受治疗加成</span><span color="#ffdfbf">-40%</span><span>。<br/>施加蕴光之茧时，扣除全队角色</span><span color="#ffdfbf">10%+1800</span><span>点生命值，若角色生命值低于</span><span color="#ffdfbf">7200</span><span>点，则改为扣除</span><span color="#ffdfbf">35%</span><span>生命值，可致命，该次扣血</span><span color="#ffdfbf">不无视</span><span>无敌帧；主动治疗清除后获得「出缠」效果。<br/>出缠：暴击率</span><span color="#ffdfbf">+15%</span><span>，造成的伤害</span><span color="#ffdfbf">+50%</span><span>，持续15s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="602" width="498" height="116" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">蕴光月守宫大招丢下的岩晶块，每层<span color="#ffe599">2.8岩</span><span>盾，共</span><span color="#ffdfbf">9</span><span>层，持续</span><span color="#ffdfbf">25s</span><span>；<br/>破坏第3/6/9层时会对鳞蜥造成</span><span color="#ffbfbf">6%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffbfbf">6%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffbfbf">18%生命值</span><span>的伤害，并瘫痪7s。<br/></span><span color="#bfffbf">(N4) </span><span>破坏月锚岩改为对月守宫造成</span><span color="#ffbfbf">4%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffbfbf">4%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffbfbf">12%生命值</span><span>的伤害。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5) </span><span>月锚岩每层的厚度变为</span><span color="#ffe599">4岩</span><span>盾，持续时间延长至</span><span color="#ffdfbf">35s</span><span>，且不再按照层数返回伤害，现击破所有9层后造成一次真伤，其值由</span><span color="#ffdfbf">10%所受伤害+70%所受岩伤</span><span>组成，不超过</span><span color="#ffdfbf">40%月守宫生命值</span><span>。瘫痪时间缩短至4s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/断玉之役-蕴光月守宫%B7根牙磐错.assets/Image_14.png')" x="1166" y="847" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
